# All software and versions on RCAC clusters

## Overview
As of **January 22, 2026**, there have been a total of **270** applications with **2470** available versions deployed across **6** RCAC HPC clusters: **ANVIL, BELL, GAUTSCHI, GILBRETH, NEGISHI, SCHOLAR**.
